@if chipDecision=="Mike"
    Player: Mike, how's everything?
    Mike: Ah, it's you! Thanks to that chip, things have been looking up. I appreciate your trust in me. How can I help you today?
    Player: Just checking in. I'm glad to see things are going well for you.
    Mike: And I'm always here if you need anything. You've made a good friend.
    
@else
