    Mike: It's you. What do you want? Can't say I'm too pleased seeing you after you decided to keep that chip away from me.
    Player: I made a choice based on what I thought was right. I hope we can move past that.
    Mike: We'll see about that. Just remember, actions have consequences.

@endif
@goto Map
